# Environment configuration for the University Scheduler.
#
# EncryptionKey is the Fernet key used to decrypt professor RUTs so they show as
# readable numbers in the schedule grid. Ask the project owner for the value.
#
# To use it: copy this file to ".env" and paste the key between the quotes, or
# simply run iniciar_scheduler.bat and paste the key when prompted on first launch.
#
# Without a valid key the app still works, but professor RUTs appear as encrypted
# tokens instead of numbers.
EncryptionKey=""
